<typeStatus id="FD5C8811AA2BFFF0B60AFAA98DCCFAF7" box="[606,654,1289,1315]" pageId="1" pageNumber="230">type</typeStatus>
locality, the Sector Mordoñal of the Vereda Peñas Blancas in which the ROGITAMA reserve is located.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
